----------------------------- File structure -----------------------------------

lib
  google_places.py -> Google Places API (radarSearch, textSearch, etc)
  websocket.py     -> Module for socket connection between application and GUI

classes
  Scanner.py   -> Scans a given area
  Scheduler.py -> Schedule for the scanner
  Limiter.py   -> Limiter(a filter) for the scanner
  Messenger.py -> A medier between GUI and application

main.py -> Main script that uses google_places.py and google_places_scanner


--------------------------------- Design ---------------------------------------

                      _________
scheduler ---------> |         | --------> GUI
                     | Scanner |    
             .---->  |_________| ----.
limiter -----'                       '---> Text


From application to GUI:
Scanner  ↔  GUI  ↔  Messenger  ↔  Websockets  ↔  JavaScript
